On Screen Display for Raspberry Pi and various sensors.


This project aims at using a Raspberry pi for On Screen Display, in FPV context for controlling a RC plane model.


This software was developed by Christian MÃ¼ller in the framework of his Master degree in software engineering at the HES-SO (http://www.hes-so.ch/en/master-engineering-610.html), under David Grunenwald supervision and Cyrille Henry mandate.


